## 🐛 Known Issues

1. **Video Player**: Currently uses placeholder div. Replace with actual video embed (YouTube/Vimeo) or HTML5 video tag
2. **Progress Tracking**: Static percentage. Connect to backend or localStorage for dynamic updates
3. **Authentication**: No login system. Integrate with university SSO or use GitHub OAuth

